1
00:00:12,910 --> 00:00:15,010
Your bureau had already classified

2
00:00:15,560 --> 00:00:17,050
Qiao Zhenxing's case as a suicide.

3
00:00:17,870 --> 00:00:19,980
What was your motive

4
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:22,170
for revisiting the timeline?

5
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,770
Dongping's a small city,

6
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:34,370
and the network of connections

7
00:00:34,790 --> 00:00:35,820
runs deep and is very complicated.

8
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:39,050
Dongping wasn't built in a day,

9
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:41,050
and neither was

10
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,730
its judicial system.

11
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:45,820
Everyone who's part of this system

12
00:00:46,790 --> 00:00:48,410
has layers of personal connections.

13
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:51,220
I doubt it's possible

14
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:53,820
that every single case in Dongping

15
00:00:54,150 --> 00:00:55,260
is squeaky clean.

16
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,050
But I can guarantee you one thing—

17
00:00:59,030 --> 00:01:01,300
we've never deliberately

18
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,580
mishandled a case.

19
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:03,820
I stand by that

20
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:05,260
with my personal integrity.

21
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:33,000
[In the Name of Justice]

22
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,000
[Episode 31]

23
00:02:44,150 --> 00:02:44,820
Mr. Cheng,

24
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,450
what did you, my brother

25
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,850
and Mr. Chen tell me three years ago?

26
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:52,730
You said I should sue Wan Hai,

27
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:54,410
and then the Freight Hub will be mine.

28
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,980
No problem, and zero cost, right?

29
00:02:58,590 --> 00:02:59,890
Is it still zero cost now?

30
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:04,260
The Task Force's arresting people,

31
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:05,980
how can you cover it up now?

32
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:07,100
First they took Sun Fei,

33
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,220
then Jiang Hongjun!

34
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,450
And did you know

35
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,820
they even questioned Li Renjun?

36
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:13,730
You didn't know?

37
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,660
Well, now you do.
Li Renjun's under the spotlight.

38
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,500
Who's next?

39
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:17,260
Huh?

40
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,820
It's Xie!

41
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,570
If they arrest him,

42
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:21,980
what are you going to do?

43
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:23,980
Long, don't you have magic touch?

44
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,260
Isn't this the time to use it?

45
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,730
C'mon, show me what you can do!

46
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,100
Tell me, when is the Task Force leaving?

47
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:29,610
Huh? What day?

48
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:30,730
Mr. Wang,

49
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,610
I know you're stressed

50
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:34,660
and uneasy.

51
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:37,340
If

52
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,010
you're okay with it,

53
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,850
I can arrange for you

54
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,060
to stay away for a while

55
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,340
until this blows over,

56
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:49,500
okay?

57
00:03:58,150 --> 00:03:59,260
Long, what are you saying?

58
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,260
You want me to

59
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:04,570
run?

60
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:07,450
Do you want me to lie low for a while,

61
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,850
or vanish for good?

62
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:12,690
Give me a number.

63
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,370
How many days should I be away?

64
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,250
Will I find that the Freight Hub
is no longer mine

65
00:04:18,270 --> 00:04:19,100
when I come back?

66
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,900
If the Wan Hai case gets overturned,

67
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,850
who's going to defend me?

68
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:36,250
Let me be crystal clear,

69
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:36,930
Mr. Chen,

70
00:04:37,510 --> 00:04:38,460
I'm not going anywhere.

71
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,730
I'm staying right here.

72
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:41,370
Mr. Chen, aren't you

73
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,220
the big shot?

74
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,610
Then do something! Get me out of this!

75
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,730
Mr. Wang, you don't need to corner me.

76
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:55,540
I told you

77
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,610
we're all in the same boat.

78
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,780
We'll figure this out together.

79
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,850
Don't be so shameless.

80
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:09,850
I'm shameless?

81
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,290
Fine, Chen Shenglong,

82
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,900
let me show you just how 'shameless'
I can be.

83
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,250
I reported Wan Hai,

84
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,780
I gave the false testimony,

85
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:20,540
and I wanted the Freight Hub, huh?

86
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,370
Fine.

87
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,850
If I really go down,

88
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:25,340
I'm taking all of you with me.

89
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,370
I'll say you were behind all of it.

90
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,700
Push me overboard,

91
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,100
and see how far your boat gets.

92
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:33,930
Xiong, calm down!

93
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:36,100
Shut up already!

94
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:36,490
What,

95
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:38,250
I'm not even allowed to vent?

96
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,370
Didn't I tell you
everything's under control

97
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,100
and we're handling it?

98
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,810
Xiong, calm down. Take it easy.

99
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,020
You got a death wish?

100
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:45,540
Sit down!

101
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:47,460
Sit down first!

102
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,250
Calm down.

103
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:56,810
Mr. Wang,

104
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,980
Xiong just had a few too many drinks.

105
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:00,490
It's no big deal.

106
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:01,810
Just some heated words. It's all fine.

107
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:02,980
Just for today,

108
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:05,250
I'm letting it slide,

109
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:06,850
on your account.

110
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:07,540
Of course.

111
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:08,580
C'mon.

112
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:09,780
Have a seat.

113
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:14,660
Mr. Wang,

114
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,050
I promise you,

115
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,660
as long as we stay united,

116
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,850
no one's getting thrown overboard.

117
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,370
Trust me.

118
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:27,460
Right, Long?

119
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,540
Mr. Wang,

120
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,900
let's keep drinking.

121
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,460
Come on.

122
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,100
To you.

123
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,170
We're here.

124
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:08,810
I lost my cool earlier.

125
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:09,900
I got a bit worked up.

126
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:12,610
Please tell Long

127
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:13,780
I didn't mean anything by it.

128
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,980
I'm just

129
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,850
a bit too stressed lately.

130
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,220
I'm kind of at my limit.

131
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:19,020
I get it.

132
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,850
Really.

133
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:21,050
But Yu, listen to me,

134
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,460
you don't need to worry.

135
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,250
Long wouldn't take it to heart.

136
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:26,490
You spoke your mind,
that's what brothers do.

137
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,980
We'll face it together.

138
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,370
Now that's what I like to hear.

139
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,370
How many years have we worked together—

140
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,250
three, four?

141
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:35,980
We've been through everything, right?

142
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,370
Yeah.

143
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,490
And come on, I don't believe

144
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,370
those punks can really

145
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:40,580
wipe out the entire

146
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,810
Dongping political and legal system,

147
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,540
and all those officers!

148
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,290
It's impossible, right?

149
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,250
Yeah, you're absolutely right.

150
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:49,850
Yu, let me be honest with you.

151
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,810
Long is only after Wan Hai's mine

152
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:53,340
for his mentor, Yu Tiancheng.

153
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,460
And you know
who Yu Tiancheng is working with?

154
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:57,980
Jiang Yuan.

155
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,660
You know what kind of power he's got.

156
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:03,780
They are both Long's backers.

157
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,370
Think about it,

158
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:06,580
how long have Long and his mentor

159
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,020
been running things in Dongping?

160
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,580
This is nothing but a small ripple.

161
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,290
I don't know

162
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,850
why I couldn't see this earlier.

163
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:17,610
Who really calls the shots here, right?

164
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:18,050
Yeah!

165
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:18,780
When you go up,

166
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:21,460
please tell Long that

167
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,050
I owe him my life.

168
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,050
Yu, that's so touching.

169
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:26,980
Alright, take care.

170
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,900
- See you around.
- Alright, bye.

171
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,100
And please pass the message to Long.

172
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,700
Of course.

173
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,250
Don't forget!

174
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:31,220
- Bye.
- Bye.

175
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,220
See you around.

176
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,130
- Bye!
- Good night!

177
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:33,940
- Bye.
- Alright, bye.

178
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:35,650
Drive, now.

179
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:37,770
Goodbye!

180
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,460
See you around!

181
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:43,940
Step on it.

182
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:03,180
Yu,

183
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:05,100
why do you look so rattled?

184
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,370
What did you talk about?

185
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:07,250
Run,

186
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,340
now.

187
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,700
I know too much.

188
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:12,980
Are you sure
you're not overthinking this, Yu?

189
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,580
It's all clear to me now.

190
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:17,010
Chen Shenglong

191
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,370
is setting me up to take the fall.

192
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,250
Stop. It's fine.

193
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:20,060
Here, take it.

194
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:21,610
Take it.

195
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,370
Keep it for yourself.

196
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:25,980
No, Yu, take it.

197
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,580
No, I don't want it. Listen to me,

198
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,770
find somewhere to lay low
for a few days.

199
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:30,850
I'll contact you

200
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:31,940
once I'm all settled.

201
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,100
No time to waste.

202
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:33,370
But...

203
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:33,820
I gotta go now.

204
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,180
Yu,

205
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,010
maybe you're overthinking this?

206
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:36,850
Is it possible that you...

207
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:40,850
Mr. Wang,

208
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:42,180
where are you headed

209
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,530
at this hour?

210
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:46,890
Nowhere.

211
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:50,220
Mr. Chen wants to see you.

212
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:52,980
Yu, run!

213
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:49,890
Watch it!

214
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,980
Mr. Wang, come on down.

215
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:57,460
What are you doing?

216
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:58,820
- Get out of my car!
- Come out!

217
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,130
Don't force me to come up.

218
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:13,820
Wang Yu!

219
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:36,300
Excuse me.

220
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:37,770
Come in.

221
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,100
Hello, Mr. Xu.

222
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,530
We're the special Task Force

223
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:45,460
and will be asking you some questions.

224
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:46,820
Okay.

225
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:48,490
Mr. Xu,

226
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,460
the Task Force

227
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,530
has detained two police officers

228
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,420
from your precinct

229
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:55,370
for investigation

230
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:56,980
recently.

231
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,650
Let's start with Jiang Hongjun.

232
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:02,300
What do the Dongping Municipal
Bureau of Public Security

233
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:03,490
and you personally

234
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,370
think of this officer?

235
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:06,980
It's shocking.

236
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:11,130
An officer at Jiang Hongjun's level

237
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,130
had over

238
00:12:12,390 --> 00:12:14,060
three million in cash in his home?

239
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:15,490
Mr. Xu,

240
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:16,180
sorry to interrupt,

241
00:12:17,150 --> 00:12:20,130
but where did you get the information

242
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,530
that over three million in cash

243
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:24,730
was found in Jiang Hongjun's home?

244
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,580
Sun Fei, the second officer

245
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,130
you detained,

246
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:30,530
told me that information.

247
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,530
Before he was taken away,

248
00:12:32,550 --> 00:12:33,490
he came to my office,

249
00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:35,300
hoping I could pull some strings
at the provincial office

250
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,100
and help him out.

251
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,890
I remember telling him that...

252
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,460
You practically fought

253
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:42,580
to take on those cases.

254
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,250
I only entrusted

255
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:49,180
the cases to you out of trust,

256
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,770
and even more so because
Ms. Lan trusted you.

257
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:55,300
But you have let down

258
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,770
both the bureau and Ms. Lan.

259
00:12:58,270 --> 00:12:59,890
So your only option is to

260
00:13:00,510 --> 00:13:01,220
cooperate with the investigation

261
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:02,530
and accept the facts.

262
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,340
That's the gist of it.

263
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,300
According to our investigation,

264
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:07,980
you did some work that

265
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,460
actually helped the case in private.

266
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:12,420
Why did you keep it private?

267
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:20,100
Let me put it this way,

268
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,130
in this line of work,

269
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:24,730
I've learned that some cases

270
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:26,530
are extremely sensitive.

271
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,980
One misstep could disrupt
the whole case.

272
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,300
Sometimes I investigate discreetly

273
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,530
to avoid
derailing the overall investigation.

274
00:13:35,510 --> 00:13:36,580
Considering that

275
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:37,850
Jiang Hongjun,

276
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:40,460
a low-ranking officer,

277
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:41,610
accepted confirmed bribes

278
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:44,130
totaling over 3.2 million,

279
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,370
and Sun Fei is implicated
in various problems—

280
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:50,060
both of which occurred under your watch—

281
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:51,460
what do you

282
00:13:52,630 --> 00:13:53,370
consider your responsibility

283
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,850
as chief of the Dongping Municipal
Bureau of Public Security?

284
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:58,460
Hong Liang,

285
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:01,730
I'll speak from the heart,

286
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,730
anyone who's been in this line of work

287
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:04,530
knows what matters most:

288
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:05,490
it's results.

289
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,130
That means solving cases
and solving them fast.

