706
00:36:39,360 --> 00:36:40,170
and the mine's value shot up.

707
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:42,170
Another one

708
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,460
was thirteen years ago.

709
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:46,460
Thirteen years ago,

710
00:36:46,880 --> 00:36:49,650
you absorbed Dacheng Mining next door,

711
00:36:50,510 --> 00:36:53,090
