763
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,300
It's not Wang Yu

764
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:00,460
who's truly after you,

765
00:39:02,030 --> 00:39:02,820
but Chen Shenglong

766
00:39:03,670 --> 00:39:04,780
and his Tianlong Company.

767
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:11,900
Thirteen years ago,

768
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,460
Dacheng Mining

769
00:39:17,110 --> 00:39:18,050
was right next to Wanchuan Mining.

