00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:35,980
Then Yu Tiancheng

798
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,460
left Dongping

799
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:38,900
for good.

800
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:43,980
So, tell me,

801
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:50,130
after thirteen years of mining

802
00:40:51,150 --> 00:40:52,050
and two deaths,

803
00:40:53,400 --> 00:40:55,300
