807
00:41:04,710 --> 00:41:05,780
when you mentioned me

808
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:09,090
and Yu Tiancheng to him last time.

809
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:12,860
Don't blame me.

810
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,210
Blame the previous generation.

811
00:41:19,480 --> 00:41:20,300
So I believe,

812
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:21,900
once this storm passes,

813
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:24,940
