814
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:26,010
Work together my ass!

815
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:30,050
My dad was framed by you!

816
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:33,010
My dad is not mafia,

817
00:41:33,550 --> 00:41:34,740
