818
00:41:34,760 --> 00:41:35,690
nor I!

819
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:37,340
You're the real mafia,

820
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:38,650
Chan Shenglong!

821
00:41:41,150 --> 00:41:41,570
You,

822
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:43,090
you,

823
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:44,650
and you.

