827
00:41:55,840 --> 00:41:57,380
Why are you still holding back?

828
00:41:58,840 --> 00:41:59,530
Ma'am,

829
00:42:00,190 --> 00:42:01,460
please don't push me.

830
00:42:06,760 --> 00:42:07,780
